&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trust us, the Juice is worth the squeeze.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Juice goes live for operators in August 2026. After years of building and running games at scale, we&#39;re opening the full portfolio to the wider market for the first time. That portfolio includes three studios players already know: Twist, Massive and Knucklehead. As our Account Manager at Juice, you own the day-to-day relationships with a portfolio of B2B operator accounts. You are responsible for keeping those operators active, engaged, and growing, ensuring they launch our content, run promotions, and see measurable value from the Juice catalogue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll build with us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on commercial role. You will manage your accounts end-to-end: from onboarding new operators through to running QBRs, coordinating promotional campaigns, and surfacing commercial opportunities. You work closely with the Director on account strategy and with product, compliance, and integrations teams to make sure operators get what they need, when they need it. You are the daily face of Juice to your operators, and the voice of those operators back into the business.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We know that innovation ignites when we build and create together, in person. This is a full-time remote opportunity based in Europe where . You’ll work right where it all happens, surrounded by our fearless crew shipping high-impact work.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who is Juice?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Juice is a B2B iGaming provider with one audacious goal: to be one of the best game providers in the world. We&#39;re not starting from zero. Juice brings together four world-class studios Twist, Massive, Knucklehead and Monstrums, all under one roof, with a catalogue of hundreds of proven titles already loved by millions of players. Each studio keeps its own creative identity; Juice gives operators a single integration, a single commercial relationship, and a unified release pipeline. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What makes us different? A ready-made catalogue. Hundreds of quality games built over years, not a roadmap, a shelf. Game verticals nobody else has. Mystery Boxes, where players win real-world prizes and operators earn higher margins. VOD games, where AI-crafted characters play out real scenarios decided by RNG, a format with nothing like it in the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The impact you’ll make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Ownership &amp;amp; Relationship Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the day-to-day relationship for an assigned portfolio of B2B operator accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for your operators; responsive, informed, and proactive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong working relationships with operator counterparts across commercial, marketing, and compliance functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a deep understanding of each operator&#39;s business: their lobby, their players, their priorities, and their competitive position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retention &amp;amp; Commercial Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive net revenue retention across your portfolio, tracking performance, identifying risks early, and acting before issues escalate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and execute upsell opportunities: new titles, verticals, premium features, and exclusive content deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain account development plans for each operator, tracking milestones and commercial targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead regular account reviews, presenting performance data, surfacing opportunities, and aligning on roadmap priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
